author: deepal
msg: If some service class want to return multiple objects (Java does not allow that) , Axis1 has concept of holder.
But if service class want to return multiple object he can do that by creating Object array by putting all those object and return that
and our RPCMessageReceiver will serialize that into multiple parts and send to the client.
